      <pattern name="Fluent v9 component consumption" location=".claude/patterns/ui/fluent-v9-component-authoring.md">
        Consume shared `TagFilter` via barrel import; pass controlled `selected` + `onChange`; do NOT re-implement.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Memoized metadata fetch" location="src/client/pcf/SemanticSearchControl/SemanticSearchControl/services/DataverseMetadataService.ts">
        Fetch option set once per mount via `useEffect` + memo; cache by entity+attribute.
